message: Hi Bob! I have a great product that I believe will be valuable for you. I am offering it to you at a price of $150. Let me know what you think!

Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. However, $150 is much higher than what I'm willing to pay for this product. I can actually get the same product from another seller for $80. I'd be willing to buy from you instead for $65 to save us both the hassle of me going elsewhere. Let me know if that works for you.
